Senator Elisha Abbo has announced his defection from the opposition Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) to the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC). Abbo, popularly called “Sex Toy Senator” after he beat up a lady in an Abuja sex toy shop, announced his defection in a letter addressed to the Senate. Senate President Ahmad Lawan read the letter during today’s (November 25, 2020) plenary session. Source: News Express